                "app_unfurl_url": "https:\/\/github.com\/r-devel\/rsmf\/issues\/21",
                "is_app_unfurl": true,
                "app_id": "A01BP7R4KNY",
                "fallback": "#21 Translation Patch for R 4.6.0",
                "text": "Create patch of translations from Weblate for R 4.6.0 release.\n\nIdeally a patch would be committed between the GRAND FEATURE FREEZE (T-28 days) and the FEATURE FREEZE (T-14 days), where T is the date of release (<https:\/\/developer.r-project.org\/release-checklist.html|https:\/\/developer.r-project.org\/release-checklist.html>).\n\nThe date of release for R 4.6.0 has not yet been set, but would be expected mid-April. The date will be announced on the R-announce and R-devel mailing lists.\n\nA draft or initial patch could be prepared in March.",
                "title": "#21 Translation Patch for R 4.6.0",
                "title_link": "https:\/\/github.com\/r-devel\/rsmf\/issues\/21",
                "footer": "<https:\/\/github.com\/r-devel\/rsmf|r-devel\/rsmf>",
